 of a series of papers where we set a framework for\ncomparability between mock catalogues and observations with a particular focus\non cluster surveys. The Euclid and LSST mocks are made publicly available in\nthe following link: http://photmocks.obspm.fr/.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2015 21:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2015 20:00:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-16"}
