 in the shape of the\ntotal XLF is primarily driven by the changing mix of unabsorbed and absorbed\npopulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2015 21:00:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2015 11:07:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2015 09:28:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 8 May 2015 17:26:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-11"}
