ful in hydraulic\nengineering applications, for which typically $2.5\\leq F\\leq 6.0$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2015 22:47:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2015 15:05:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-12"}
